extendedInfo.description: Gadgets, Gizmos and Machinery. This is the Steampunk GOContacts Theme. Not much more to say except...You need GO Contacts Ex to install and use this theme. There are two Go Contacts in the play store. Please be sure to install the Go Contacts EX version - from here:https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jbapps.contactproIf Steampunk is your thing take a look at my:Steampunk GO Launcher themeSteampunk GO SMS themeSteampunk GO Keyboard themeSteampunk GO Locker ThemeSteampunk GO Locker Light themeSteampunk GO Contacts themeSteampunk GO Search WidgetSteampunk GO Calendar WidgetSteampunk GO Twitter WidgetSteampunk GO Facebook WidgetSteampunk GO SMS PopUpSteampunk Go Contacts WidgetSteampunk Message Widget... and more to comeThere's also a bunch of extra free downloads on my website (mindseed.co.za), extra wallpapers, docks and iconsThank you, I hope you like this as much as my others, please rate in the market, it's really appreciated and makes all the time it takes making these, even more worth it. Thanks - be kind to a dev near you ;)If there is anything you would like to suggest or comment on for any of my themes, please send me an email - I reply to all emails within a few hours and I'm an insomniac - so it gives me something to read.Follow: https://twitter.com/@mindseedDesignLike: http://www.facebook.com/mindseed.designPlus: https://plus.google.com/109275982008448960608/postsVisit: http://www.mindseed.co.zaEmail: mindseed.design@gmail.comKeywords: steampunk, steampunk android theme, android steampunk theme, industrial theme, steampunk theme,

reviews.title: Samsung Galaxy S3
reviews.comment: I cannot get this to work on my samsung galaxy s3. As a matter of fact none of the steampunk widgets work on this phone. I cant find them plus they keep force closing. What is up with that? I love this theme for my phone and the widgets as well. Please fix for SGS3. Anyone else having problems with these widgets on a samsung galaxy s3? If you got it working, tell me how you did it, please.

reviews.comment: Contacts, Phone, Keyboard, and SMS pop-up, all seamlessly provide me with a constant Steampunk theme through the whole experience, and not once do I see the generic stock screens when using this (widget too) - Great Job here pulling it all together.

reviews.title: Lovely to look at!
reviews.comment: I saw these steampunk themes in the Play store, fell in love, and downloaded EVERYTHING \"Go\" so I could use it! I am not kidding. Used other apps for sms, launching, etc before. Now all is \"Go\" so I can see these beautiful pieces of art all day long. I especially like the Blue steampunk... Hope there is more coming!

reviews.title: What a shame
reviews.comment: There\'s no reason why they can\'t allow this app to be used without Go Launcher! I have Go Next Launcher but of course this won\'t work with it. I had to stop using Go Launcher as it kept freezing up my phone and slowed it way down and after getting no help or response from Go Dev Team I finally uninstalled it. NONE OF GO LAUNCHERS STUFF WORKS ON NEXT LAUNCHER EVEN THO IT\'S A GO PRODUCT. DUMB & GREEDY!! Not calling you greedy, but Go Launcher for making Go stuff not work on Next Launcher. I lost lots cash..

reviews.comment: Amazing. I can\'t wait to see what you do next. I really like this...you never disappoint.
